50|$|The <b>Warning</b> <b>Decision</b> Training Division (WDTD), {{known as}} the <b>Warning</b> <b>Decision</b> Training Branch until April 1, 2015, {{is one of three}} {{training}} organizations in the NWS Training Division which also includes the Forecast Decision Training Branch and the NWS Training Center. WDTD develops and delivers training on the integrated elements of the warning process within a National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration (NOAA)/National Weather Service (NWS) forecast office. WDTD instructors develop and deliver a variety of in-residence, teletraining, and on-line asynchronous training content.|$|E
